Why?

00:36:47.359 --> 00:36:48.359
Because I want to use it.

00:36:48.359 --> 00:36:51.679
I want to be the best that I can be, not so that anyone would look at me and say, they

00:36:51.679 --> 00:36:52.679
should be lifted up.

00:36:52.679 --> 00:36:56.279
But also that people would say, this is God's grace.

00:36:56.279 --> 00:37:00.959
That God would be glorified and then deploy it, use it for God's glory.

00:37:00.959 --> 00:37:06.319
Look for those opportunities, seize those opportunities to be used for God's glory.

00:37:06.319 --> 00:37:07.319
Let's pray.

00:37:07.319 --> 00:37:08.359
Father, we love you.

00:37:08.359 --> 00:37:09.759
We thank you so much for loving us.

00:37:09.759 --> 00:37:15.119
We thank you for the spiritual gift, Lord, that you've given to each of us.

00:37:15.119 --> 00:37:16.799
We thank you for the truth of your Word.

00:37:16.799 --> 00:37:22.919
And I pray that you would help us as your people, Lord, to truly desire to know what

00:37:22.919 --> 00:37:25.959
our spiritual gift is, that God, you would reveal it to us.

00:37:25.959 --> 00:37:29.559
If maybe there's some here tonight that just don't know what their spiritual gift is, God,

00:37:29.559 --> 00:37:34.479
I pray that you would just lay upon their heart a desire to know it, Lord, to be able

00:37:34.479 --> 00:37:36.679
to discover what their spiritual gift is.

00:37:36.679 --> 00:37:40.239
Maybe there's some that know what their spiritual gift is, but they're just simply not using

00:37:40.239 --> 00:37:42.799
it, God, at this time for your glory.

00:37:42.799 --> 00:37:45.039
I pray that you'd stir us, Lord.

00:37:45.039 --> 00:37:51.199
Help us, even as Paul instructs Timothy, to stir up the gift that is in us, to rekindle,

00:37:51.199 --> 00:37:57.319
to redetermine that we will use the gift that you've bestowed upon us for your glory, that

00:37:57.319 --> 00:38:00.799
we would be good stewards of the manifold grace of God.

00:38:00.799 --> 00:38:04.199
I pray that in the moments of invitation that you'd have your will and way, that you would

00:38:04.199 --> 00:38:08.319
work in hearts and lives as only you can, and we'll thank you for it in Christ's name.

00:38:08.319 --> 00:38:09.319
We pray.

00:38:09.319 --> 00:38:09.319


